Installation instructions
=========================
You need the following programs:

- GNU make
- bash

Firstly, clone the repository.

  $ git clone https://github.com/system32149/termux-color

Go to the directory:

  $ cd termux-color

Then run make:

  $ make install

Uninstalling
============
To uninstall, run this command on the termux-color directory
you cloned the repository to:

  $ make uninstall

